 309:middlewares/freertos/source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM4F/port.c ****             /* Determine the maximum priority from which ISR safe FreeRTOS API
 310:middlewares/freertos/source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM4F/port.c ****              * functions can be called.  ISR safe functions are those that end in
 311:middlewares/freertos/source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM4F/port.c ****              * "FromISR".  FreeRTOS maintains separate thread and ISR API functions to
 312:middlewares/freertos/source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM4F/port.c ****              * ensure interrupt entry is as fast and simple as possible.
